  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nAfter version 3.4.11, the build output json file doesn't have event topic. \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. install version 3.4.11 \r\n2. ```truffle init``` generate default MetaCoin contract.\r\n3. ```truffle migrate``` to deploy the contract\r\n4. check build/contract/MetaCoin.json. At the end of file, you will see something like this\r\n```\r\n  \"networks\": {\r\n    \"32150\": {\r\n      \"events\": {\r\n        \"0xddf252ad1be2c89b69c2b068fc378daa952ba7f163c4a11628f55a4df523b3ef\": {\r\n          \"anonymous\": false,\r\n          \"inputs\": [\r\n            {\r\n              \"indexed\": true,\r\n              \"name\": \"_from\",\r\n              \"type\": \"address\"\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n              \"indexed\": true,\r\n              \"name\": \"_to\",\r\n              \"type\": \"address\"\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n              \"indexed\": false,\r\n              \"name\": \"_value\",\r\n              \"type\": \"uint256\"\r\n            }\r\n          ],\r\n          \"name\": \"Transfer\",\r\n          \"type\": \"event\"\r\n        }\r\n      },\r\n      \"links\": {\r\n        \"ConvertLib\": \"0x871bf4a25d3c97ce0018be2025d02320d5efe5d2\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"address\": \"0x7f6c216534308cd777b2445ee57e98b7ab92f5f0\",\r\n      \"updated_at\": 1513827011034\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n5. install version 4.0.0-beta.1\r\n6. do step 2, 3, 4 again.\r\n7. In build/contract/MetaCoin.json, no event topics. looks like this:\r\n```\r\n  \"networks\": {\r\n    \"32150\": {\r\n      \"events\": {},\r\n      \"links\": {\r\n        \"ConvertLib\": \"0x681667163878ed16a67ede3ba248b1f8825193f5\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"address\": \"0x28064071ba26b2639ad5bb69e9dafdb7e6e4855b\"\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nNeed event topic in build contract json file.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nNo event topic.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System:  MacOS High Sierra\r\n* Truffle version: 4.0.x (tryied 4.0.3, 4.0.4, same result)\r\n* Ethereum client: geth 1.7.3\r\n* node version: v8.5.0\r\n* npm version: 5.6.0\r\n\r\n\r\n@gnidan ",
